{"tid":660840,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"痛苦嘅龜頭炎","createTime":"2018-05-11T04:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T14:33:14.000Z","uid":107954,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1402d72afb8f0794c91705302a46de0341963378","tid":660840,"uid":107954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:52:26.000Z","msg":"各位巴打 有冇試過keep住 復發龜頭炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我3個星期前龜頭炎 睇完醫生<br />\n佢開左抗生素俾我食 同開藥俾我擦<br />\n咁吃完一個禮拜後見好番<br />\n就冇再擦到d藥 （clotrimazole)<br />\n到左尋日 又復發開始癢<br />\n病徵同上次一樣<br />\n想問我可唔可以繼續擦上次醫生開俾我隻藥<br />\n好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6babb74fa9dbafa5b6251d3d7f16f978dc61503f","tid":660840,"uid":78379,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:54:56.000Z","msg":"影幾張相（多角度）上黎睇下，大家一齊幫你斷症"},{"pid":"6ef730dd8ad00bc40f38821692a96ec7110c05b3","tid":660840,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:56:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>影幾張相（多角度）上黎睇下，大家一齊幫你斷症</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32646c300a043146f92d99f8cb7bc1ecfb85998","tid":660840,"uid":68081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6babb74fa9dbafa5b6251d3d7f16f978dc61503f","tid":660840,"uid":78379,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:54:56.000Z","msg":"影幾張相（多角度）上黎睇下，大家一齊幫你斷症"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:58:06.000Z","msg":"識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc3a458244eeea2a54cbfb720d123702ba936bc","tid":660840,"uid":13287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:58:35.000Z","msg":"龜頭炎會點